{"tid":2414832,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"德國內政部首度揭露　中共動用國家組織施壓當地流亡港人","createTime":"2021-02-19T17:02:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T09:05:37.000Z","uid":204533,"like":444,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"693c2df61a3e136950ffc4955ba4cc31ecda713f","tid":2414832,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T17:02:52.000Z","msg":"德國內政部周五（19日）首度承認，中共國家組織向流亡到德國的香港人施壓。<br />\n<br />\n德國內政部在回覆反對派自由民主黨（FDP）議員查詢的聲明中指出，「自香港示威活動開始...德國境內的中國國家組織便嘗試行動，以有利中國政府為出發點影響大眾對事件的觀感」，更包括「<strong><span class=\"red\">對支持示威人士採取行動...親中共的中國公民多次在德國公共場所和網路上破壞示威活動」。聲明更引述2019年8月17日漢堡一次集會為例，參加集會人士遭反對示威者拍照和拍片，認為此舉「相信旨在恐嚇」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n自由民主黨議員詹森（Gyde Jensen）說：「這是聯邦政府首次承認中國共產黨的觸手已伸到德國，內政部特別是情報部門應該制訂策略，有效保護流亡德國的中國公民和香港人。」（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"48a136c55a8865c330d781aad8a97a55c2da708d","tid":2414832,"uid":204533,"like":87,"dislike":3,"score":84,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T17:03:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210219/VJU3ZC2RKFFY3OAH3VH4QFCX5Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210219%2FVJU3ZC2RKFFY3OAH3VH4QFCX5Y%2F&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGhjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=aabd00ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210219%2FVJU3ZC2RKFFY3OAH3VH4QFCX5Y%2F&h=4f197f2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210219/VJU3ZC2RKFFY3OAH3VH4QFCX5Y/</a>"},{"pid":"81cdb7e915e7cde49edd522e8b1a8b06cd0df54c","tid":2414832,"uid":7369,"like":224,"dislike":4,"score":220,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T17:04:58.000Z","msg":"隔咗成年幾先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b0e008817199e2deb710315168bc84920d0eae","tid":2414832,"uid":204533,"like":304,"dislike":2,"score":302,"quote":{"pid":"81cdb7e915e7cde49edd522e8b1a8b06cd0df54c","tid":2414832,"uid":7369,"like":224,"dislike":4,"score":220,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"20